-- Gold Futures Advance in Newe York, Erasing Earlier Drop of as Much as 0.9%
-- Patrick McKiernan
-- 2010-06-29T16:06:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/gold-futures-advance-in-newe-york-erasing-earlier-drop-of-as-much-as-0-9-.html

          
          
             Gold futures for August delivery
rose $2.80, or 0.2 percent, to $1,241.40 an ounce at 12:06 p.m.
on the Comex in New York. Earlier, the metal dropped as much as
0.9 percent.  
          
          


  


        